00:33:29.820 --> 00:33:31.820
And they had to take on more girls,

00:33:31.820 --> 00:33:33.820
but I had that promotion,

00:33:33.820 --> 00:33:36.820
and seven and six pence a week,

00:33:36.820 --> 00:33:38.820
increasing my wages.

